{
	"info": {
		"name": "E-Commerce API",
		"description": "## E-Commerce API\n\nAPI لمتجر إلكتروني مبني بـ Express + Prisma + PostgreSQL\n\n### القاعدة\n```\n{{base_url}}/api\n```\n\n### المصادقة\n- **Access Token** (صلاحية 15 دقيقة) يُرسل في Header:\n  ```\n  Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}\n  ```\n- **Refresh Token** (صلاحية 7 أيام) يُستخدم في `/api/auth/refresh`\n\n### متغيرات Postman\n- `base_url`: `http://localhost:3000` (غيّرها حسب تشغيلك)\n- `accessToken`: يُحدّث تلقائياً بعد Login\n- `refreshToken`: يُحدّث تلقائياً بعد Login",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:3000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "accessToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "refreshToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "productId",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "productSlug",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "categoryId",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "categorySlug",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "orderId",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "🔐 Auth",
			"description": "المصادقة وإدارة المستخدمين",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "تسجيل مستخدم جديد",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"أحمد علي\",\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\",\n  \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						},
						"description": "تسجيل مستخدم جديد (CUSTOMER أو ADMIN)\n\n**التحقق:**\n- name, email, password مطلوبون\n- الإيميل يجب أن يكون صالحاً\n- كلمة المرور 6 أحرف على الأقل\n\n**الاستجابة:** 201\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": { \"id\": \"...\", \"name\": \"...\", \"email\": \"...\", \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\" },\n    \"accessToken\": \"...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "تسجيل الدخول",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', jsonData.data.refreshToken);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"ahmed@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "تسجيل الدخول — يُعيد Access Token + Refresh Token\n\n**التحقق:**\n- email و password مطلوبان\n\n**الاستجابة:** 200\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": { \"id\": \"...\", \"name\": \"...\", \"email\": \"...\", \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\" },\n    \"accessToken\": \"...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "تحديث Access Token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', jsonData.data.accessToken);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/refresh",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "refresh"]
						},
						"description": "استخدام Refresh Token للحصول على Access Token جديد\n\n**الاستجابة:** 200\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"...new...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "الملف الشخصي",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
						},
						"description": "جلب بيانات المستخدم الحالي (يتطلب توكن)\n\n**الاستجابة:** 200\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"...\",\n    \"name\": \"...\",\n    \"email\": \"...\",\n    \"role\": \"CUSTOMER\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"...\"\n  }\n}\n```"
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
